2. Component Responsibilities
Component	Responsibility	Key Libraries
Next.js Frontend	URL input, progress display, reader UI, export triggers	React 19, TanStack Query, lucide-react
FastAPI Backend	REST API, job lifecycle, pipeline orchestration	FastAPI, Pydantic v2, SQLAlchemy 2.0
Extractor Module	URL validation, metadata fetch, subtitle download	yt-dlp (Python API), bilibili-api-python
Transcription Module	Audio download, conversion, ASR	yt-dlp, ffmpeg, faster-whisper
Chunking Module	Segment transcript into semantically coherent chunks	Custom (recursive char split + overlap)
Summarization Module	Map-reduce LLM summarization, structured output	openai SDK (OpenAI-compatible)
Export Module	Render results to Markdown / TXT / JSON	Jinja2 templates
Database	Job state, cached results, transcripts	SQLite + SQLAlchemy (swap to PostgreSQL later)
3. Technology Choices
Layer	Choice	Rationale
Frontend framework	Next.js 15 (App Router)	SSR/SSG, file-based routing, React Server Components
Backend framework	FastAPI	Async-native, auto OpenAPI, Pydantic validation
ORM	SQLAlchemy 2.0 + Alembic	Async support, migration tooling, DB-agnostic
Database (MVP)	SQLite	Zero-config, single-file, swap to PG via env var
ASR engine	faster-whisper	CTranslate2 backend, 4× faster than vanilla Whisper, int8 support
Video/audio tool	yt-dlp	Best Bilibili support, Python API, active maintenance
Audio processing	ffmpeg	Industry standard, required by faster-whisper
LLM client	openai Python SDK	Compatible with OpenAI, Deepseek, local Ollama, etc.
Task queue (future)	Celery + Redis or arq	Async job processing for multi-user; MVP uses asyncio.create_task
Package manager (Python)	uv	Fast, reliable, replaces pip + venv
Package manager (JS)	pnpm	Fast, disk-efficient, workspace support
