7. Inter-Service Communication
From → To	Protocol	Notes
Frontend → Backend	HTTP REST + SSE (optional)	JSON payloads; SSE for real-time progress (stretch)
Backend → Bilibili	HTTPS	Via yt-dlp / bilibili-api-python; rate-limited
Backend → LLM API	HTTPS	OpenAI-compatible endpoint; configurable via env
Backend → SQLite	Local file I/O	Async via aiosqlite
Backend → ffmpeg	Subprocess	Audio conversion
Backend → faster-whisper	In-process Python	Loaded on first ASR request, kept in memory
